    <item>
      <title>Create Personal Blog Using Hugo</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/create-personal-blog-using-hugo/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 20:09:18 +0530</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/create-personal-blog-using-hugo/</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-hugo&#34;&gt;What is Hugo?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hugo is a fast and flexible &lt;strong&gt;static site generator&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offers a wide range of &lt;strong&gt;cool themes&lt;/strong&gt; to customize your site.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Write in Markdown&lt;/strong&gt; and see your content rendered beautifully on your website.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;steps-to-build-your-blog&#34;&gt;Steps to Build Your Blog&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-install-hugo&#34;&gt;1. Install Hugo&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install Hugo on your system:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Linux/macOS&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;brew install hugo
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows&lt;/strong&gt;: Download the executable from Hugo&amp;rsquo;s GitHub releases. (need to add the link here)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-create-a-new-website-project&#34;&gt;2. Create a New Website Project&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Run the following command to create your project:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
